---
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import '../styles/global.css';

---
<section>
  <div class="banner d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center container-fluid" style="background: linear-gradient(25deg, #0a0908, #1a237e, #4fc3f7); min-height: 80vh; position: relative;">
    <!-- Animated background elements -->
    <div class="code-background">
      <div class="code-line">{'{'}</div>
      <div class="code-line">{'  '}<span class="code-keyword">"nombre"</span>: <span class="code-string">"TekohaTech"</span>,</div>
      <div class="code-line">{'  '}<span class="code-keyword">"especialidad"</span>: <span class="code-string">"Soluciones Web"</span>,</div>
      <div class="code-line">{'  '}<span class="code-keyword">"misión"</span>: <span class="code-string">"Innovar en digital"</span></div>
      <div class="code-line">{'}'}</div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 text-center banner-content">
      <h1 class="gradient-text mt-4 mb-4 section-title">TekohaTech</h1>
      <p class="h5 text-light-contrast mt-2 mx-auto px-3 px-md-5" style="max-width: 900px;">
        "Bienvenido! Tekoha significa 'pueblo' o 'comunidad' en guaraní, reflejando nuestro compromiso de ofrecerte servicios de diseño y desarrollo web que te ayuden a destacar en línea. Lleva tu presencia en la web al siguiente nivel con nosotros."
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4">
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Comienza tu proyecto</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  .gradient-text {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #4fc3f7, #2196f3, #00e676); /* New color palette */
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .code-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    opacity: 0.1;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: #ffffff;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .code-line {
    margin: 2px 0;
    animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .code-line:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
  .code-line:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }
  .code-line:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.6s; }
  .code-line:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.8s; }

  .code-keyword {
    color: #ff6b6b;
  }

  .code-string {
    color: #4fc3f7;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }

  .banner-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: #00e676;
    border-color: #00e676;
    color: #1a237e;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #00c853;
    border-color: #00c853;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 230, 118, 0.3);
  }
</style>